{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"qj2rqad3fu03nbzrzybffsr","title":"Design Systems","desc":"","updated":1647478947669,"created":1647398584322,"custom":{},"fname":"web.frontend.design-systems","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"522adc66a61ec87d01d552900e074242","links":[],"anchors":{"design-tokens":{"type":"header","text":"Design Tokens","value":"design-tokens","line":14,"column":0,"depth":3},"references":{"type":"header","text":"References","value":"references","line":18,"column":0,"depth":4}},"children":[],"parent":"RhPwsgMN0xuoggGXxjHXh","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"design-systems\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#design-systems\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Design Systems</h1>\n<p>Design Systems exist to create a source of truth for a product design. Some notable design systems:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Google's <a href=\"https://material.io/\">Material UI</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://atlassian.design/\">Atlassian</a></li>\n<li>IAG's <a href=\"https://chromadesignsystem.com/\">Chroma</a></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"design-tokens\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#design-tokens\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Design Tokens</h3>\n<p>Design tokens are a way to store styles so that they can be re-used by any platform e.g. web or mobile</p>\n<h4 id=\"references\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#references\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>References</h4>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://zure.com/blog/collaboration-with-design-tokens-and-storybook/\">https://zure.com/blog/collaboration-with-design-tokens-and-storybook/</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"wn8PE1RhG0znK1alrGFYv","title":"Knowledge Garden","desc":"","updated":1645656788117,"created":1631901573363,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"r